  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] these were obviously years of extreme well-being and happiness for us children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, some crazy things come back to my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] our upbringing was rather militaristic, as you can imagine, with the background of my father as by his choice a professional soldier.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he always really maintained the-- the attitudes and the allures of a soldier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So needless to say, we picked that up and our main toys were-- had to do with soldiery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had whole armies built up on the floor in our rooms, and shot at these was little canons that had pencils, you know, preferably shooting off the heads of these little [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] soldiers.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they were made of not plastic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This preceded plastic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Plaster?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was plaster probably, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, that was one of the things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we-- we also dressed ourselves in uniforms with sabers and whatnot and battled with our friends, preferably with the lights out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Surprisingly, everybody survived that with all the eyes in a place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- we were fanatics about going to the zoo, and discovered that the favorite food of monkeys were live meal worms.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we-- we went sort of every-- every afternoon to-- or whenever we could with our governess to the-- to the zoo, bringing bags full of-- of live meal worms.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
